ikrs.typesystem
Class BasicArrayType

java.lang.Object
  ikrs.typesystem.BasicTypeAdapter
      ikrs.typesystem.BasicArrayType
All Implemented Interfaces:
BasicType
public class BasicArrayType
extends BasicTypeAdapter
implements BasicType

The BasicArrayType is a not so basic type class with the capability to wrap a set to BasicType instances together into a linear array-like list. All access methods guarantee constant runtime, so the class does not support item removal.
